OL,3,CMan arrested over death of ice hockey
OL,4,Cplayer is rebailed
OL,6,FA man who was arrested over the death
OL,7,Fof an ice hockey player during a match
OL,8,Fin Sheffield has been rebailed.
OL,10,FAdam Johnson died on October 28 last
OL,11,Fyear after being hit in the neck by an
OL,12,Fopposition player's skate during a
OL,13,Fmatch at Sheffield's Utilita Arena.
OL,15,FThe 29-year-old American, who was
OL,16,Fplaying for Nottingham Panthers
OL,17,Fagainst , died in hospital.
OL,19,FA post-mortem examination confirmed he
OL,20,Fdied as a result of a neck injury.
