OL,3,CMan arrested over death of ice hockey
OL,4,Cplayer is rebailed
OL,6,FA man was arrested on suspicion of
OL,7,Fmanslaughter in November and then
OL,8,Fbailed by South Yorkshire Police.
OL,10,FOn Thursday he was rebailed until June
OL,11,F26, the force confirmed in a statement.
OL,13,FIt added: "Adam's loved ones remain at
OL,14,Fthe forefront of our minds as this
OL,15,Fcomplex investigation continues."
OL,17,FMr Johnson's death shocked the ice
OL,18,Fhockey world, especially as the
OL,19,Fincident was witnessed by thousands of
OL,20,Ffans at the arena in Sheffield.
